#: ../../../docs/crates/sphinx-rustdocgen/directives.rst:12
msgid ""
"The module primarily provides the :rust:enum:`Directive`, which implements "
"the various directives using directive specific structs. The enum and all "
"directive specific structs implement both :rust:trait:`~sphinx_rustdocgen::"
"formats::RstContent` and :rust:trait:`~sphinx_rustdocgen::formats::"
"MdContent` traits. It also provides the :rust:enum:`DirectiveOption` enum, "
"which implements the various options of the directive."
